<span id="freeTextContainer14289580674186630964">The Grass Harp is a wonderful story.<br/>The other stories in the book have a variety of themes, some of which I enjoyed more than others, but I am impressed with the quality of Capote&apos;s writing in all of them.</span>
  <span id="freeText14289580674186630964" style="display:none">The Grass Harp is a wonderful story.<br />The other stories in the book have a variety of themes, some of which I enjoyed more than others, but I am impressed with the quality of Capote's writing in all of them.</span>
